---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "../components/container.astro";
import Sectionhead from "../components/sectionhead.astro";
import Pricing from "../components/pricing.astro";
---

<Layout title="Product A - YOLOVibe">
  <Container>
    <Sectionhead>
      <Fragment slot="title">3-Day AI Coding Mastery Workshop</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        Transform your development workflow with comprehensive training on leading AI coding assistants including Windsurf, Cursor, GitHub Copilot, and emerging platforms. Learn universal AI coding principles that work across all tools.
      </Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight">
        Master AI-Powered Development
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg mt-4 text-slate-600">
        This intensive 3-day workshop teaches you how to effectively use AI coding assistants like Windsurf, Cursor, GitHub Copilot, and other leading platforms to accelerate your coding process and build better software faster.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 mx-auto max-w-4xl mt-12">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-2xl text-gray-800">What You'll Master</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-slate-500 text-lg">
          Learn platform-agnostic AI coding principles and tool-specific techniques for maximum productivity.
        </p>
        <ul class="grid mt-6 text-left gap-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-1 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Universal AI coding principles that work with any platform</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-1 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Hands-on experience with Windsurf, Cursor, and GitHub Copilot</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-1 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Advanced prompt engineering for optimal AI assistance</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-1 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Building voice-to-CLI interfaces with AI coding tools</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-1 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Rapid application scaffolding and prototyping techniques</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-2xl text-gray-800">Advanced Integration</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-slate-500 text-lg">
          Enterprise-ready AI coding implementation for your organization.
        </p>
        <ul class="grid mt-6 text-left gap-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-1 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Multi-tool workflow strategies for maximum efficiency</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-1 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Team collaboration with AI coding assistants</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-1 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Adapting AI tools to your organization's security requirements</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-1 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Custom AI tool configuration and optimization</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-1 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Future-proofing your AI development skills</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-center mb-8">3-Day Learning Journey</h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-blue-100 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">1</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">AI Coding Foundations</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Master universal AI coding principles, prompt engineering, and platform comparison across Windsurf, Cursor, GitHub Copilot, and emerging tools.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-green-100 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-600">2</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Advanced AI Integration</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Deep dive into CLI automation, voice interfaces, and multi-tool workflows for maximum development velocity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-purple-100 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-600">3</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Enterprise Implementation</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Deploy AI coding solutions in your organization with security, compliance, and team collaboration best practices.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-24">
      <Pricing />
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>
